metadata.name: Virtual Soldier
metadata.description:
Virtual Soldier 1/1
In the future all gamers are soldiers. They are equipped with the standard greens and a VR headset. The headset merges physical and virtual reality. They have no way of knowing the difference and kill for fun thinking it's all a game!

This is AI generated art using Stable Diffusion method. This is all prompt and no touchups except for enhanced resolution to increase the size. 
#painting #scifi #gamer #gaming #fantasy #AI #VR #color #digital
